Kunegama lesiNgisi elisebenza kakhulu lika-“remedial action”, elisho ukuthatha isinyathelo sokulungisa. Sengathi abaningi balihumusha sengathi uMvikeli woMphakathi ukhuluma nge-“punitive action”, okusho isinyathelo sokujezisa. Kuze kukhulunywe nangokuba uMengameli axoshe ungqongqoshe. Mina ngicabanga ukuthi uMvikeli woMphakathi ukhuluma ngokuba uMengameli enze ungqongqoshe aphalazise uMnuz Pillay imali axhawulwa ngayo “kungafanele”.  UMhlehlebuli uMfo kaMaSwid’abhaliwe eSayidi